gService (间接影响)\n```\n\n### 3. 延迟模式分析\n- **productcatalogservice** 的延迟异常最为显著，符合根因特征\n- **shippingservice** 和 **emailservice** 的延迟可能是下游依赖productcatalogservice间接导致\n- **recommendationservice** 的延迟相对轻微，可能是系统整体负载增加的结果\n\n建议优先检查productcatalogservice的资源使用情况、数据库连接池状态以及TiDB数据库性能。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "21950e63-387", "component": "tidb-tikv", "reason": "io_util and region_pending spike causing database latency", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(tidb-tikv)", "observation": "io_util P99 increased from 0.07 to 0.4, region_pending median increased 142%"}, {"step": 2, "action": "TraceAnalysis(21950e63-387)", "observation": "productcatalogservice queries to TiDB showing high latency"}, {"step": 3, "action": "LogSearch(tidb-tikv)", "observation": "No error logs found, silent IO degradation"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
